frames.caption: A young boy and his dog sit on a grassy hill, gazing at the starry night sky and a large planet. The city lights twinkle in the distance, creating a serene and contemplative atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil night setting where a boy and his dog are enjoying a peaceful moment under the stars. They are seated on a hill overlooking a city, with a prominent planet visible in the sky.

frames.caption: An astronaut sits on a rocky outcrop beside a dog, gazing at a distant planet under a starry sky. The scene is set in a vast, alien landscape with rolling hills and a glowing horizon. The atmosphere is serene and contemplative, with the cosmos providing a stunning backdrop.
frames.description: The scene depicts an astronaut and a dog on an alien planet, observing the night sky and a distant celestial body. The setting is otherworldly, with expansive terrain and a cosmic vista.
